*Došli* smo u park prije nego što je počela kiša. (We came to the park before it started to rain.) 

*Došla* je učiteljica u klasu ranije nego što je bilo planirano. (The teacher came to the class earlier than it was planned.)

Nekoliko nam je sati *došlo* da dovršimo zadatak. (We had a few hours to finish the task.)

*Došlo* nam je do ušiju da su se oni rastali. (We heard that they had broken up.)

*Došli* su iz daleke zemlje pre nekoliko godina. (They arrived from a distant country a few years ago.)